      "content": "hey so i've been taking these antibiotics for a skin infection for like 3 days now and my skin looks totally normal again. the redness is gone and it doesn't hurt anymore. is it okay if i just stop taking them now? i dont really want to keep putting all these chemicals in my body if i dont need to.",
