      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i mean, the infection is literally gone. if the bacteria are already dead, then wouldn't continuing the pills just be a waste of time? i've read that taking more than you need can actually be bad for your liver and stuff. wouldn't it be safer to just stop once the symptoms are totally gone?",
