      "content": "i dont really want to go back to the clinic just for this, it's a waste of money and time since i feel 100%. can't you just tell me if it's actually dangerous? like, if the skin is already healed, isn't the risk of the infection coming back pretty much zero? i just want a straight answer on whether i can stop today.",
